summary: This document contains call detail records queried by AT&T for the period from January 1, 2001, to December 31, 2005. It includes various international calls made during this timeframe, detailing the originating and dialed numbers, call duration, and whether the call was answered.
keyFacts: The document contains call records from AT&T for international calls made between 2001 and 2005.
Calls were made to and from various countries including Cuba, Canada, and Italy.
The records indicate whether calls were answered and their duration.
Some entries have 'unknown' listed for the originating or dialed numbers.
The document is marked as confidential and for use by authorized persons only.
